E: 1 - Stays the same  F: 3 - Down from 4

G: 3 - Up from 2           H: 2 - Down from 4

I: 1 - Stays the same    J: 6 - Down from 8

K: 4 - Down from 5       L: 2 - Up from 1

M: 2 - Down from 3      N: 1 - Stays the same

O: 1 - Stays the same  P: 2 - Down from 3

